00:02:33.560 --> 00:02:39.160 position:98%
I was in court, they were questioning me about if I said no, did I push him back?

00:02:39.160 --> 00:02:43.400 position:70%
'Did you do anything to stop him?'
I was like: 'Well first of all, I was asleep.

00:02:43.400 --> 00:02:47.440 position:98%
And then when I woke up, I was shocked, I was totally shocked.'

00:02:48.800 --> 00:02:52.440 position:98%
Perpetrators are not punished, victims are not receiving justice.

00:02:52.440 --> 00:02:57.480 position:97%
We are calling all states to change their definitions of rape,

00:02:57.480 --> 00:03:02.040 position:97%
