00:03:02.680 --> 00:03:05.000 position:70%
Convictions in Denmark are astonishingly low.

00:03:05.000 --> 00:03:08.040 position:83%
The government estimates more than 5,000 women a year

00:03:08.040 --> 00:03:10.240 position:59%
